variant_descriptions.KADDW: Add 16 bits masks in k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KADDB: Add 8 bits masks in k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KADDQ: Add 64 bits masks in k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KADDD: Add 32 bits masks in k2 and k3 and place result in k1.

op.text: Adds the vector mask k2 and the vector mask k3, and writes the result into vector mask k1.
